{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "乡愁夜空下绽放之花第4话 被封印的灾厄",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "王子等人打倒了他们认为的元凶——魔兽，\\n然而龙脉泉却仍是枯竭状态。\\n原来真正的元凶是100年前\\n被封印起来的强大魔兽瓦尔法雷。\\n为打倒巨型魔兽，众人前往异界空间。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "太好了！打倒了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊，平息了异变，\\n魔力源点也能恢复原状吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110268_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "应该是……\\n但总觉得怪怪的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "唔……有点诡异啊……\\n总之先回去蓬莱大人身边吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔、唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那个……难道是异界裂缝！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不好，黑暗魔力溢出来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "蓬莱大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "不行！别过来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯，很危险。如果接触到黑暗魔力，\\n不知道会受到什么样的影响……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "为什么会变成这样……\\n不是已经打倒\\n引起异变的魔兽了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "老夫的判断有误……\\n真正的异变并非龙脉泉的枯竭。\\n真正的异变……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "是瓦尔法雷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "瓦尔法雷！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "那是100年前老夫和徐福\\n合力封印的魔兽……\\n老夫没发现它的封印已经开始解除……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "如果这片土地的魔力\\n是受刚才的魔兽所影响……\\n那倒好了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "瓦尔法雷是被贪欲驱使，\\n不断吞噬魔力的魔兽。\\n只要它还有魔力，就无法打倒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "所以，老夫和徐福将它封印在\\n没有正常魔力的世界……\\n也就是异界空间里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "然而在这100年间，\\n它似乎得到了足以从异界空间\\n向龙脉泉伸出魔爪的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "不过之前的魔兽\\n扭曲龙脉泉的魔力却起到了\\n延缓瓦尔法雷复活的效果……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "什么！也就是说我们打倒了魔兽，\\n才造成了这样的结果吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "不，事情变成这样是老夫的责任。\\n所以老夫要在这里阻止它！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "不过为了以防万一……\\n就拜托你们保护蓬莱小镇了。\\n带着大家逃去安全地带吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "蓬莱大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔唔唔唔唔唔唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "瓦尔法雷！老夫绝不会让你\\n对老夫珍爱的孩子们出手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "既然如此，只好豁出去了！\\n让老爷子独自拼命，\\n可不符合我的性格！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110268_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "同感！\\n我正想说这话呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊，我们一起冲进异界空间，\\n打倒瓦尔法雷吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "别做蠢事！那可是老夫和徐福\\n从前费了九牛二虎之力\\n才封印成功的凶恶敌人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "说我们都是您的孩子的，\\n不正是蓬莱大人嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "所谓孩子，就是要超越父母的存在。\\n我现在就要证明这一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔唔唔……哈哈哈！\\n“大人反被小孩教”，原来如此！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "你说的没错！\\n孩子就是要超越父母的存在！\\n而且俗话说“玉不琢，不成器”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "好，老夫不会再多说什么！\\n唯有信任孩子们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "客人们，孩子们就拜托了。\\n有继承了龙之血的你在这里，\\n便会多一份希望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，只要是我能做到的，\\n一定拼尽全力。不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我并不觉得自己是客人。\\n因为瓦尔法雷的存在\\n绝不仅是蓬莱小镇的问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊。如果置之不理，\\n它没准会成为这整片大陆的灾难。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没错。这也是我们的战斗，\\n必须得讨伐它才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n老夫这种老家伙会下意识地竖起高墙，\\n而打破壁垒正是你们的长处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "那就……拜托你们了，世界的孩子们啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位，我们上！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}